links.title: Twist Bioscience Announces Closing of Upsized Public Offering of Common Stock and Full Exercise of Underwriters' Option to Purchase Additional Shares
links.description: SOUTH SAN FRANCISCO, Calif.--()--Twist Bioscience Corporation (NASDAQ: TWST), a company enabling customers to succeed through its offering of high-quality synthetic DNA using its silicon platform, today announced the closing of its underwritten public offering of 3,211,362 shares of its common stock at a public offering price of $110.00 per share, which consists of 3,136,362 shares sold by Twist, including the exercise in full by the underwriters of their option to purchase up to an additional 409,090 shares of common stock in the offering, and 75,000 shares sold by certain selling stockholders.
